parameters:
Noblewoman Caron: Today, Lord Hays will be returning home!
Let's invite Dalsa and Amina-chan and celebrate.
Young Louis: Yay! I wonder if Father will take me hunting?

Noblewoman Caron: Yes, of course. Louis has been working
hard on his studies and training.

Young Louis: I'm looking forward to it! I hope he comes
back soon!

The world surrounding young Louis during his childhood was
perfect. His strong and kind father, Hays. The well-mannered
maid, Dalsa. A slightly mischievous but sister-like figure,
Amina.

And above all, his mother Caron, who was kind and
beautiful. They were the guarantors of Louis' perfect
world.

Louis grew up in a gentle cradle and learned the manners of
a noble, the ways of a warrior, and the basics of magic.

Louis' goal was to be praised and recognized by his loved
ones. This desire would later lead to an obsession with his
mother, Caron.
